VBA 要怎麼改

目前你的 Dictionary 只記錄：

groups(groupKey)(branchLabel) = allocation

只知道每個月份需要多少筆，

不知道前面月份已經拿了多少筆。

所以要先累加每個分行已使用的 CNT。

⸻

建議新增一個 Dictionary

在

Dim finalSqlBuilder As String

前面加：

Dim branchOffset As Object
Set branchOffset = CreateObject("Scripting.Dictionary")

⸻

產生條件時改成

原本：

For Each branchLabelVariant In branchConditions.Keys
    condList.Add "BRNCH_NBR = '" & branchLabelVariant & _
                 "' AND CNT <= " & branchConditions(branchLabelVariant)
Next branchLabelVariant

改成：

For Each branchLabelVariant In branchConditions.Keys
    Dim startCnt As Long
    Dim endCnt As Long
    Dim allocCnt As Long
    allocCnt = CLng(branchConditions(branchLabelVariant))
    If branchOffset.Exists(branchLabelVariant) Then
        startCnt = branchOffset(branchLabelVariant) + 1
    Else
        startCnt = 1
    End If
    endCnt = startCnt + allocCnt - 1
    condList.Add _
        "(BRNCH_NBR = '" & branchLabelVariant & _
        "' AND CNT BETWEEN " & startCnt & _
        " AND " & endCnt & ")"
    branchOffset(branchLabelVariant) = endCnt
Next branchLabelVariant

