2. 將 Group Key 排序

在：

For Each groupKeyVariant In groups.Keys

前面新增：

Dim sortedKeys() As String
Dim keyCount As Long
Dim x As Long, y As Long
Dim tempKey As String
keyCount = groups.Count
ReDim sortedKeys(0 To keyCount - 1)
x = 0
For Each groupKeyVariant In groups.Keys
    sortedKeys(x) = CStr(groupKeyVariant)
    x = x + 1
Next
For x = 0 To UBound(sortedKeys) - 1
    For y = x + 1 To UBound(sortedKeys)
        If sortedKeys(x) > sortedKeys(y) Then
            tempKey = sortedKeys(x)
            sortedKeys(x) = sortedKeys(y)
            sortedKeys(y) = tempKey
        End If
    Next y
Next y

然後把：

For Each groupKeyVariant In groups.Keys

改成：

For x = 0 To UBound(sortedKeys)
    groupKeyVariant = sortedKeys(x)

並把最後的：

Next groupKeyVariant

改成：

Next x

